information: La Vannerie d’Aujourd’hui is located in Fayl-Billot in the heart of the Haute Marne's traditional basket weaving area. Our family business, which has 5 generations of hand-crafting experience behind it, proposes a wide choice of quality wickerwork "Made in France" made on our premises and also imported products: rattan baskets, wicker baskets, mushrooming baskets, baskets for chestnuts, wicker baskets, shopping bags, log cart for stairs, animal baskets and beds, wicker animal carriers, rattan lounge furniture, rattan easy chairs, wicker linen chest, rattan mirror, wickerwork containers and packaging, raw materials, etc... La Vannerie d’Aujourd’hui also repairs your old baskets and rattan furniture to give them a second lease of life. We are on hand to welcome both private and trade customers and work all over France and abroad.
